_sText: zm_storage_grafa Zombies escaped from Pisspot corp. Almost all people died, but small group of surivors camped in small storage. But zombies are unstoppable and they got through walls and now they trying to eat surivors brains. Surivors: Defend for round time or kill all zombies. Zombies: Eate brains of all surivors. Original map by Grafa. Max players: 30 Install instructions You need to install all files with zm_storage_grafa name including bsp and txt file!!! Effects used: HDR 3D skybox shadow control env_tonemap_controller anti decompile prop_physics prop_physics_override prop_physics_multiplayer prop_static overlays etc. THX for download and Have Fun Add Feedback and donate me :) And dont forget to make good assessments
